***Eric’s Echo Chamber – House Rules***
1️⃣ **Respect the Vibes** – We’re all friends here, so don’t be a jerk. Keep it chill.
2️⃣ **No Drama, No Stress** – This isn’t a soap opera. If you have beef, take it elsewhere.
3️⃣ **Inside Jokes Stay Inside** – What happens in the Echo Chamber stays in the Echo Chamber. No leaks!
4️⃣ **Don’t Spam (Unless It’s Funny)** – Memes, chaos, and nonsense are welcome—but don’t overdo it.
5️⃣ **Eric’s Word is Law (Kinda)** – At the end of the day, Eric makes the rules. Deal with it.
6️⃣ **No Ghosting** – If you disappear for too long, expect some lighthearted bullying when you return.
7️⃣ **Invite-Only** – If you want to bring someone new in, ask first. No randoms.
8️⃣ **Have Fun (Or Else)** – Seriously, if you're not having fun, what are you even doing here?
